title: Black Female Gospel (Various 2007-2014)
description:
Here is a nice collection (my own compilation) of black female Gospel songs. This wasn't a deliberate project, but after I had collected all I was looking for I seen what I had. These are all purchased songs from a few different digital sites: Amazon, iTunes ... There are 30 songs total and each with it's own individual cover art.

Enjoy and please seed if you can. Also, if you like an artist support them and buy their songs.
